It's hot! It's hot! Help!

62
00:05:34,330 --> 00:05:36,530
Wait, Big Sis! Don't pull me!

63
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:42,330
Big Sis Sonia! Watch out!

64
00:05:42,330 --> 00:05:45,490
